This paper deals with improving the Age of Information (AoI) in status update systems, which is a topic related to networked systems and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves queueing theory and stochastic processes, which are topics related to information theory and probability theory, respectively. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.PF (Probability) are also likely categories. The paper also discusses the trade-off between average and average peak AoI, which is a topic related to control systems and optimization. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another likely category. Finally, the paper uses numerical methods to obtain results, which is a topic related to computational mathematics. Therefore, cs.MA (Numerical Analysis) is also a likely category.
